0airport%20authority.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20people%20are%20dead%20after%20a%20Boeing%20747%20cargo%20plane%20landing%20at%20Hong%20Kong%20International%20Airport%20veered%20off%20the%20runway%20and%20into%20the%20sea%20on%20Monday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20statement%20from%20Hong%20Kong's%20civil%20aviation%20department%2C%20the%20incident%20happened%20at%20around%203%3A50%20a.m.%20local%20time.%20The%20department%20said%20the%20flight%2C%20which%20was%20arriving%20from%20Dubai's%20Al%20Maktoum%20International%20Airport%2C%20had%20%26quot%3Bdeviated%20from%20the%20North%20Runway%20after%20landing%20and%20ditched%20into%20the%20sea.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20skidding%2C%20the%20plane%20%26quot%3Bcrashed%20through%20the%20fencing%26quot%3B%20and%20collided%20with%20an%20airport%20security%20patrol%20car%2C%20pushing%20the%20car%20into%20the%20sea%2C%20said%20Steven%20Yiu%20Siu-Chung%2C%20executive%20director%20for%20Hong%20Kong's%20airport%20operations%2C%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Monday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20security%20staff%20members%20aged%2030%20and%2041%20were%20in%20the%20car.%20One%20was%20certified%20dead%20at%20the%20landing%20site%2C%20while%20the%20other%20was%20declared%20dead%20at%20a%20hospital%2C%20Yiu%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20during%20the%20Monday%20press%20conference%20that%20the%20patrol%20vehicle%20had%20been%20a%20safe%20distance%20from%20the%20runway%20before%20the%20collision.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYiu%20said%20the%20car%20was%20%26quot%3Boutside%20the%20fences%26quot%3B%20and%20patrolling%20a%20route%20around%20the%20airport's%20northern%20coast%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bdefinitely%20did%20not%20run%20out%20onto%20the%20runway.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20had%20also%20been%20no%20distress%20signal%20from%20the%20cargo%20plane%2C%20Yiu%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20ground%20security%20officers%20had%20worked%20at%20the%20airport%20for%20seven%20and%2012%20years%20re