phone%20and%20speaking.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e339d35dbc4fd10daa37aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221450%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESteven%20Qiu%20founded%20RoboSense%20in%202014.%20RoboSense%20had%20the%20world's%20largest%20market%20share%20for%20passenger%20car%20LiDAR%20systems%20in%202024%2C%20per%20the%20market%20research%20company%20Yole%20Group.%3Cp%3EFutureChina%20Global%20Forum%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESteven%20Qiu%20is%20the%20founder%20and%20chief%20scientist%20of%20Chinese%20LiDAR%20maker%20RoboSense.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EQiu%20said%20a%20multi-sensor%20system%20is%20safer%20than%20a%20vision-only%20system%20for%20self-driving%20vehicles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20long%20criticized%20LiDAR%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bexpensive%20and%20unnecessary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESteven%20Qiu%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Chinese%20LiDAR%20maker%20RoboSense%2C%20says%20a%20multi-sensor%20system%20is%20a%20better%20and%20safer%20approach%20for%20self-driving%20vehicles%20than%20the%20vision-only%20system%20touted%20by%20Tesla%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiDAR%2C%20which%20stands%20for%20Light%20Detection%20and%20Ranging%2C%20is%20a%20sensor%20that%20scans%20the%20environment%20by%20emitting%20laser%20beams%20and%20measuring%20the%20time%20it%20takes%20to%20get%20a%20return%20signal.%20LiDAR%20can%20be%20found%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWaymo's%20robotaxis%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20consumer%20products%2C%20like%20robot%20vacuums%20and%20smartphone%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20debate%20over%20whether%20a%20vision-only%20or%20multi-sensor%20approach%20is%20better%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20self-driving%20vehicles%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years%20or%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20Qiu%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20FutureChina%20Global%20Forum%20held%20in%20Singapore%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20by%20now%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20everyone%20understands%20that%20a%20vision-only%20approach%20is%20not%20safe%20enough.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20corner%20cases%20that%20a%20vision-only%20system%20cannot%20account%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQiu%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20vehicles%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20achieve%20Level%203%20or%20Level%204%20driving%20automation%20capability%20with%20a%20vision-only%20system.%20He%20added%20that%20other%20sensors%2C%20including%20LiDAR%2C%20need%20to%20be%20added%20to%20the%20mix%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20standards%20organization%20SAE%20International%20ranks%20automation%20systems%20from%20Level%201%20to%205.%20Level%201%20systems%20can%20only%20provide%20basic%20assistance%2C%20like%20automatic%20braking%20and%20lane-keeping%2C%20while%20Level%205%20systems%20can%20drive%20a%20vehicle%20in%20all%20conditions.%20Tesla's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-fsd-diary-curiosity-amazement-shock-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFull%20Self-Driving%20software%3C%2Fa%3E%20requires%20human%20supervision%20and%20is%20a%20Level%202%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20say%20you%20are%20cruising%20on%20an%20expressway.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20white%20car%20that%20has%20stopped%20in%20front%20of%20you%2C%20it%20would%20be%20challenging%20for%20a%20vision-only%20system%20to%20tell%20if%20it's%20a%20car%20or%20a%20white%20cloud%20in%20the%20sky%2C%26quot%3B%20Qiu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSimilarly%2C%20if%20you%20are%20driving%20toward%20a%20tunnel%2C%20the%20system%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20if%20there's%20a%20black%20car%20driving%20ahead%20of%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoboSense%2C%20founded%20in%202014%2C%20had%20the%20world's%20largest%20market%20share%20for%20passenger%20car%20LiDAR%20systems%20in%202024%2C%20market%20research%20group%20Yole%20Group%20said%20in%20a%20report%20published%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22739cc492-729b-4866-889c-eda068946bb9%5C%22%3EMusk%3A%20LiDAR%20is%20'expensive%20and%20unnecessary'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20long%20been%20a%20critic%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-lidar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELiDAR%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20as%20recently%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1959831831668228450%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAugust%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20April%202019%2C%20Musk%20said%20at%20Tesla's%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-autonomy-investor-day-live-updates-event-details-elon-musk-self-driving-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAutonomy%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20event%20that%20automakers%20will%20eventually%20stop%20using%20LiDAR%20technology%20on%20their%20self-driving%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20should%20point%20out%20that%20I%20don't%20actually%20super%20hate%20LiDAR%20as%20much%20as%20it%20may%20sound%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20SpaceX's%20Dragon%20spacecraft%20uses%20LiDAR%20to%20navigate%20and%20dock%20at%20the%20International%20Space%20Station.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20cars%2C%20it's%20friggin%20stupid.%20It's%20expensive%20and%20unnecessary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20you%20solve%20vision%2C%20it's%20worthless.%20So%20you%20have%20expensive%20hardware%20that's%20worthless%20on%20the%20car.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQiu%20said%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20LiDAR%20systems%20has%20fallen%20significantly%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20from%20about%20%2470%2C000%20per%20vehicle%20to%20around%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20performance%20capabilities%20of%20LiDAR%20systems%20have%20also%20increased%20as%20their%20cost%20continues%20to%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20views%20on%20LiDAR%20appear%20to%20be%20in%20the%20minority%20among%20auto%20executives.%20Ford%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-ceo-china-completely-dominating-tesla-gm-ford-ev-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJim%20Farley%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20at%20the%20Aspen%20Ideas%20Festival%20in%20June%20that%20his%20company%20views%20LiDAR%20as%20%26quot%3Bmission%20critical.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20a%20reflection%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20truck%20or%20the%20sun%20in%20the%20camera's%20eyes%20where%20the%20camera%20will%20be%20completely%20blinded%2C%20the%20LiDAR%20system%20will%20see%20exactly%2C%26quot%3B%20Farley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELi%20Xiang%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Chinese%20EV%20maker%20Li%20Auto%2C%20said%20at%20his%20company's%20%26quot%3BAI%20Talk%26quot%3B%20event%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Elast%20year%20that%20Musk%20cannot%20see%20the%20value%20of%20LiDAR%20because%20American%20and%20Chinese%20traffic%20conditions%20are%20vastly%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20drive%20in%20China%20at%20night%2C%20you%20will%20often%20see%20trucks%20with%20broken%20tailights%2C%20or%20even%20trucks%20without%20working%20tailights%2C%20just%20parked%20on%20the%20road%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20existing%20camera%20systems%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20detect%20these%20trucks%20from%20afar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20if%20Musk%20were%20in%20China%2C%20and%20driving%20on%20various%20highways%20late%20in%20the%20night%2C%20he%20would%20choose%20to%20include%20LiDAR%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobosense-steven-qiu-elon-musk-self-driving-lidar-camera-problem-2025-1