and%20a%20wave%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eyoung%20professionals%3C%2Fa%3E%20starting%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20boom%20that's%20driving%20Taiwan's%20place%20in%20the%20global%20economy%20is%20also%20drawing%20sharp%20lines%20between%20who%20can%20afford%20to%20build%20a%20life%20and%20who%20can't.%20In%20Hsinchu's%20wealthiest%20boroughs%2C%20parenting%20is%20a%20high-investment%2C%20high-competition%20pursuit.%20But%20rising%20housing%20costs%20and%20inequality%20are%20pricing%20many%20young%20locals%20out%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20visit%20to%20Hsinchu%20in%20late%20May%2C%20I%20found%20glossy%20new%20high-rise%20housing%20lining%20the%20tracks%20as%20my%20high-speed%20rail%20train%20pulled%20into%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zhubei%2C%20Hsinchu%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6852dfbb3d5881a51c1baa7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZhubei%2C%20Hsinchu%3Cp%3EHuileng%20Tan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20mall%2C%20I%20watched%20an%20elementary%20schooler%20casually%20pay%20for%20his%20solo%20lunch%20at%20the%20next%20table%2C%20while%20I%20balked%20at%20my%20%2425%20bill%20at%20a%20bougie%20French%20caf%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20I%20go%20to%20Hsinchu%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20there%20are%20so%20many%20kids%20around%20and%20wonder%20if%20we%20really%20have%20a%20low%20birthrate%2C%26quot%3B%20my%20friend%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b1cc41c0-5ed3-472e-8b1e-0e51422a0a93%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETech%20jobs%20bring%20stability%20%E2%80%94%20and%20babies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETaiwan's%20total%20fertility%20rate%2C%20or%20TFR%2C%20hit%20just%200.87%20per%20woman%20in%202023%20%E2%80%94%20holding%20steady%20from%202022%20after%20seven%20straight%20ye