ing%20town%2C%20Hsinchu%20has%20transformed%20into%20Taiwan's%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20TSMC%20employees%20alone%20accounted%20for%20at%20least%202%25%20of%20all%20children%20born%20in%20Taiwan%2C%20despite%20making%20up%20just%200.3%25%20of%20the%20island's%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigher%20fertility%20and%20migration%20have%20made%20Hsinchu%20city%20and%20county%20the%20only%20two%20administrative%20regions%20in%20Taiwan%20with%20more%20young%20than%20old%20people%2C%20according%20to%20Taiwan's%20interior%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChip%20and%20tech%20companies%20in%20Hsinchu%20typically%20hire%20engineers%20out%20of%20graduate%20school%2C%20so%20they%20would%20be%20in%20their%20late%2020s%20when%20they%20start%20working%20for%20these%20firms.%20This%20is%20the%20prime%20age%20for%20marriage%20and%20family%20formation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Wu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECities%20like%20Taoyuan%20in%20the%20northwest%20of%20Taiwan%20%E2%80%94%20home%20to%20another%20industrial%20zone%20%E2%80%94%20also%20show%20a%20higher%20fertility%20rate%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20Taiwan%2C%20likely%20for%20similar%20reasons%2C%20said%20Wu%2C%20who%20heads%20a%20research%20institute%20on%20macroeconomic%20trends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225ccf26c3-6f7b-4c4a-a252-5ee048697920%5C%22%3ETech%20wealth%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20tech%20has%20driven%20Taiwan's%20recent%20wave%20of%20wealth%2C%20most%20people%20aren't%20in%20semiconductors.%20About%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20workforce%20%E2%80%94%20are%20in%20the%20lower-paid%20service%20sector%2C%20official%20data%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20gap%20helps%20explain%20why%20Hsinchu%2C%20and%20especially%20its%20tech%20workers%2C%20are%20thriving%20while%20much%20of%20the%20country%20falls%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Guanxin%20borough%20near%20Hsinchu's%20tech%20zone%20has%20been%20Taiwan's%20wealthiest%20district%20for%20five%20straight%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%