feng%20Non-profit%20Kindergarten.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chiang%20Chung-hwa%2C%20the%20principal%20of%20Gaofeng%20kindergarten%20in%20Hsinchu%2C%20Taiwan%20at%20his%20workplace.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6852dd7d3d5881a51c1baa0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChiang%20Chung-hwa%2C%20the%20principal%20of%20Gaofeng%20kindergarten%20in%20Hsinchu%2C%20Taiwan.%3Cp%3EHuileng%20Tan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChiang%20said%20his%20preschool%20aims%20to%20develop%20kids%2C%20typically%20age%20three%20to%20six%2C%20holistically%2C%20instead%20of%20focusing%20on%20academics.%20Even%20then%2C%20what%20parents%20sign%20their%20kids%20up%20for%20after%20school%20is%20out%20of%20his%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20pressure%2C%20even%20when%20your%20kids%20are%20still%20small%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20as%20kids%20ran%20up%20to%20us%2C%20swinging%20from%20his%20arm%20before%20meeting%20their%20parents%20to%20go%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20that%20pressure%20comes%20from%20moms'%20informal%20networks%20%E2%80%94%20sharing%20tips%2C%20organizing%20classes%2C%20and%20helping%20with%20admissions.%20Many%20of%20these%20women%20have%20moved%20to%20Hsinchu%20from%20other%20cities%20for%20their%20husbands'%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20competition%20starts%20early.%20Chang%20recalled%20an%20interview%20at%20a%20prestigious%20elementary%20school%20where%20both%20parents%20and%20children%20were%20evaluated%20via%20an%20interview%20and%20playtime%20observation.%20They%20didn't%20get%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChang%20said%20she%20wasn't%20disappointed%20by%20the%20setback%20because%20they%20loved%20the%20school%20where%20her%20son%20ended%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cutthroat%20competition%20and%20resources%20required%20to%20raise%20children%20are%20putting%20pressure%20on%20the%20baby%20boomlet.%3C%2Fp%3