dustry%20lives%20in%20a%20future%20where%20fully%20autonomous%20entities%20collaborate%20in%20parallel%20to%20write%20all%20the%20code%20and%20humans%20are%20useless.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20doesn't%20want%20to%20live%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Karpathy's%20ideal%20future%2C%20humans%20and%20AI%20collaborate%20to%20code%20and%20execute%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20it%20to%20pull%20the%20API%20docs%20and%20show%20me%20that%20it%20used%20things%20correctly.%20I%20want%20it%20to%20make%20fewer%20assumptions%20and%20ask%2Fcollaborate%20with%20me%20when%20not%20sure%20about%20something.%20I%20want%20to%20learn%20along%20the%20way%20and%20become%20better%20as%20a%20programmer%2C%20not%20just%20get%20served%20mountains%20of%20code%20that%20I'm%20told%20works%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20con%20of%20building%20the%20kind%20of%20agents%20that%20render%20humans%20useless%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20that%20humans%20are%20then%20useless%2C%20and%20AI%20%26quot%3Bslop%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20low-quality%20content%20generated%20by%20AI%2C%20becomes%20ubiquitous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKarpathy%20isn't%20the%20only%20one%20to%20raise%20concerns%20about%20the%20functionality%20of%20AI%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20LinkedIn%20last%20year%2C%20ScaleAI%20growth%20lead%20Quintin%20Au%20talked%20about%20how%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-agents-errors-hallucinations-compound-risk-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eerrors%20agents%20make%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20compounded%20with%20every%20additional%20task%20they%20take%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCurrently%2C%20every%20time%20an%20AI%20performs%20an%20action%2C%20there's%20roughly%20a%2020%25%20chance%20of%20error%20(this%20is%20how%20LLMs%20work%2C%20we%20can't%20expect%20100%25%20accuracy)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20LinkedIn.%20%26quot%3BIf%20an%20agent%20needs%20to%20complete%205%20actions%20to%20finish%20a%20task%2C%20there's%20only%20a%2032%25%20chance%20it%20gets%20every%20step%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20skeptical%20of%20the%20current%20state%20of%20AI%20agents%2C%20Karpathy%20said%20he%20isn't%20an%20AI%20skeptic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20AI%20timelines%20are%20about%205-10X%20pessimistic%20w.r.t.%20what%20you'll%20find%20in%20your%20neighborhood%20SF%20AI%20house%20party%20or%20on%20your%20twitter%20timeline%2C%20but%20still%20quite%20optimistic%20w.r.t.%20a%20rising%20tide%20of%20AI%20deniers%20and%20skeptics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrej-karpathy-ai-agents-timelines-openai-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760905152000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67acccd87bb3f854015ca40d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrej-karpathy-ai-agents-timelines-openai-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI%20cofounder%20Andrej%20Karpathy%20said%20that%20agents%20just%20aren't%20working%2C%20and%20it'll%20take%20about%20a%20decade%20to%20get%20them%20to%20a%20place%20where%20they%20are%20useful.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40businessinsider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A49%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrej-karpathy-ai-agents-timelines-openai-2025-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98The%20Choral%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20Ralph%20Fiennes%20Conducts%20a%20Sweet-Sounding%20but%20Gently%20Rebellious%20Anti-War%20Oratorio%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760905147000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F10%2Fthe-choral-01.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236556557%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CGod%20Save%20the%20Ki