3C%2Fa%3E%20paid%20off.%20The%20no-sugar%20and%20no-red-dye%20policy%20eased%2C%20and%20now%20I%20can%20hand%20over%20a%20ring%20pop%20without%20guilt%20when%20they%20are%20with%20me.%20If%20I'd%20fought%20it%2C%20I%20might%20not%20have%20had%20the%20chance.%20Respect%20builds%20trust%2C%20and%20the%20freedom%20to%20fish%20candy%20out%20of%20my%20purse%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2269c2a135-6d0f-447d-b431-418709bd65bf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20had%20to%20set%20my%20own%20boundaries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20my%20first%20grandchild%20was%20born%2C%20I%20imagined%20the%20kids%20coming%20to%20my%20house.%20We'd%20bake%20cookies%20and%20dig%20into%20a%20special%20Grandma%20toy%20box.%20But%20my%20daughter-in-law%20pictured%20me%20coming%20to%20their%20home%20and%20helping%20in%20their%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegular%20drives%20to%20my%20grandkids'%20house%20mean%20hours%20on%20the%20road%20and%20stepping%20out%20of%20my%20own%20comfort%20zone.%20Honestly%2C%20for%20most%20of%20us%2C%20grandparenting%20begins%20at%20a%20stage%20in%20life%20when%20our%20energy%20runs%20thinner%2C%20and%20adding%20travel%20on%20top%20of%20wrangling%20little%20ones%20is%20exhausting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20difference%20in%20vision%20taught%20me%20something%20important%3A%20parents%20don't%20hold%20the%20monopoly%20on%20boundaries.%20I%20had%20to%20set%20them%20too%2C%20though%20drawing%20those%20lines%20without%20damaging%20relationships%20takes%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20we%20found%20a%20compromise.%20Most%20visits%20now%20take%20place%20at%20my%20house%2C%20which%20feels%20right%20to%20me%2C%20even%20if%20it%20leaves%20behind%20its%20own%20messes%20and%20crumbs.%20Boundaries%20aren't%20selfish.%20They're%20what%20allow%20me%20to%20show%20up%20with%20joy%20instead%20of%20exhaustion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227b950bf6-e5b0-4ded-b3e8-1c34a1e93f6d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20here%20to%20support%20the%20parents%20too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20my%20only%20job%20as%20a%20grandma%20would%20be%20to%20adore%20the%20kids.%20Instead%2C%20I've%20become%20a%20sounding%20board%20for%20stressed%20parents%2C%20listening%20to%20worries%20about%20sports%2C%20food%2C%20or%20discipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20tough%20to%20stay%20quiet%20when%20I%20see%20patterns%20from%20my%20own%20parenting%20years%20repeat.%20I%20remember%20forcing%20my%20kids%20to%20clean%20their%20plates%20and%20insisting%20they%20avoid%20certain%20TV%20shows.%20Looking%20back%2C%20not%20every%20battle%20was%20worth%20fighting.%20None%20of%20my%20children%20starved%2C%20and%20they%20all%20grew%20up%20just%20fine.%20Yet%20now%20I%20watch%20my%20kids%20wrestle%20with%20similar%20questions%20and%20make%20choices%20I%20might%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20my%20good%20intentions%20slip%20into%20helicopter%20behavior%2C%20like%20jumping%20in%20too%20quickly%20with%20advice.%20I%20have%20to%20remind%20myself%20that%20my%20%26quot%3Bhelp%26quot%3B%20can%20feel%20like%20meddling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20even%20knit%20a%20blanket%20for%20my%20granddaughter%2C%20imagining%20it%20would%20be%20her%20special%20treasure.%20Instead%2C%20it%20was%20quickly%20replaced%20with%20a%20store-bought%20version.%20That%20stung%20more%20than%20I%20expected%2C%20and%20reminded%20me%20that%20what%20feels%20meaningful%20to%20me%20may%20not%20be%20to%20her%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20thing%20that%20surprised%20me%20is%20that%20I'm%20not%20allowed%20to%20post%20photos%20of%20my%20grandkids%20online.%20Do%20you%20know%20how%20hard%20it%20is%20for%20this%20grandma%20to%20keep%20pictures%20to%20herself%3F%20Torture.%20But%20respecting%20that%20boundary%20is%20part%20of%20the%20deal%2C%20even%20if%20I%20have%20to%20brag%20without%20snapshots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remind%20myself%20often%20that%20my%20role%20isn't%20to%20fix%20everything.%20It's%20about%20listening%2C%20supporting%2C%20and%20loving%2C%20even%20when%20it%20goes%20against%20my%20instincts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224701a2dd-e878-4f46-a2eb-7d57b3c8e822%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20try%20not%20to%20compare%20myself%20to%20the%20other%20grandparents%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EModern%20families%20often%20mean%20multiple%20sets%20of%20grandparents.%20Divorce%2C%20remarriage%2C%20and%20blended%20households%20can%20create%20a%20whole%20cheering%20section.%20Some%20show%20love%20with%20gifts%2C%20others%20with%20money%2C%20and%20some%20by%20attending%20every%20single%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20not%20to%20compare.%20When%20I%20miss%20an%20event%20for%20work%2C%20I%20imagine%20my%20grandkids%20loving%20the%20other%20grandmas%20more.%20A%20wise%20friend%20reminds%20me%20that%20kids%20remember%20love%2C%20not%20attendance%20records%20or%20price%20tags.%20I%20hold%20on%20to%20that%20when%20my%20paranoia%20starts%20to%20whisper%20in%20my%20ear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20Grandma%20is%20just%20as%20wonderful%20as%20I%20had%20hoped%20it%20would%20be%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20the%20easy%20ride%20I%20imagined.%20I%20didn't%20expect%20to%20have%20so%20many%20rules%20to%20follow%2C%20boundaries%20to%20set%2C%20and%20to%20discover%20new%20insecurities%20at%20this%20phase%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20us%20think%20we've%20figured%20life%20out%20when%20we%20reach%20the%20grandma%20stage%2C%20but%20grandparenting%20is%20the%20great%20leveler.%20It%20reminds%20me%20that%20I'm%20still%20a%20work%20in%20progress.%20This%20phase%20of%20life%20is%20not%20about%20perfection.%20It's%20about%20showing%20up%2C%20listening%20hard%2C%20making%20sure%20my%20grandkids%20know%20they're%20loved%2C%20whether%20I'm%20baking%20cookies%20or%20knitting%20blankets%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20my%20handiwork%20doesn't%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20the%20treasure%20I%20imagined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-thought-being-grandma-would-be-easy-i-was-wrong-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Inside