20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20interior%20of%20a%20home%20on%20Kindred.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f3151d1c1f80efbec5d9a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20interior%20of%20a%20home%20on%20Kindred%20in%20Vancouver%2C%20Canada.%3Cp%3EKindred%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a88a0c8-a560-4899-98b4-52f2c186602b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHome%20swapping%20is%20a%20'social%20contract%2C'%20not%20a%20financial%20one%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKindred%20is%20a%20give-to-get%20marketplace.%20It's%20free%20to%20join%20and%20no%20money%20is%20exchanged%20between%20host%20and%20guest%2C%20but%20in%20order%20to%20stay%20in%20someone%20else's%20home%2C%20members%20need%20to%20offer%20up%20their%20own%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20the%20app%20connects%20people%20for%20direct%20swaps%20%E2%80%94%20for%20instance%2C%20a%20member%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20could%20swap%20their%20home%20with%20a%20member%20in%20New%20York%20for%20two%20weeks.%20Members%20can%20also%20build%20up%20credits%20by%20offering%20their%20homes%20when%20they're%20out%20of%20town%20and%20not%20staying%20at%20another%20Kindred.%20They%20can%20then%20spend%20those%20credits%20on%20nights%20at%20other%20Kindred%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPalefsky%20said%20the%20swapping%20%26quot%3Ballows%20the%20relationship%20to%20feel%20much%20more%20like%20a%20social%20contract%20instead%20of%20a%20financial%20contract.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeagan%20Cignoli%2C%20a%20sculptor%20based%20in%20West%20Hollywood%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Kindred%20is%20the%20first%20option%20she%20checks%20when%20planning%20a%20trip.%20She's%20stayed%20in%20Kindred%20homes%20in%20Portugal%2C%20Greece%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20Joshua%20Tree.%20She's%20even%20used%20it%20locally%20to%20stay%20in%20downtown%20Los%20Angeles%20or%20Santa%20Monica%20when%20she%20has%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20of%20